home.common.daily_txs.title: Daily Transactions
home.common.daily_txs.hint: Number of transactions yesterday (0:00 - 23:59 UTC). The chart displays daily transactions for the past 30 days.
home.common.daily_operational_txs.title: Daily op txns
home.common.daily_operational_txs.hint: Number of operational transactions yesterday (0:00 - 23:59 UTC). The chart displays daily operational transactions for the past 30 days.
home.common.coin_price.title: {{symbol}} price
home.common.market_cap.title: Market cap
home.common.market_cap.hint: The total market value of a cryptocurrency's circulating supply. It is analogous to the free-float capitalization in the stock market. Market Cap = Current Price x Circulating Supply.
home.common.tvl.title: Total value locked
home.common.tvl.hint: Total value of digital assets locked or staked in a chain
